title: [v0.12] panic: runtime error: integer divide by zero

labels.name: bug
labels.description: A problem with current functionality, as opposed to missing functionality (enhancement)

labels.name: frozen-due-to-age
labels.description: Issues closed and untouched for a long time, together with being locked for discussion

body:
my first test of v0.12 was not that successful, divisions by zero are always bad :laughing: 

quick workaround seems to be setting
`
<scanProgressIntervalS>-1</scanProgressIntervalS>
`
to prevent getting to the line that causes the crash, so I can at least continue testing for other errors^^
